  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting Action for Disaster Risk Governance and Working to Achieve Preparedness for Risk Reduction through Technical Assistance in Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project supports the Government of Nepal in Disaster Risk Reduction and Management (DRRM). IOM aims to support the establishment of a robust legal framework at provincial and municipal levels. Further, this project contributes to strengthening the operational capacity of the National Disaster Management Authority, through trainings to their staff and to elected representatives and government officials, at provincial and municipal levels. Thematics of the trainings will include drafting of DRRM acts and policies, including emergency preparedness.</narrative>
  </description>
